<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Pinboard GPT" description="Privacy policy for Pinboard GPT browser extension">
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
    <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> / Pinboard GPT
  </p>

  <h1>Pinboard GPT Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Pinboard GPT is a browser extension that allows users to pin, organize, and save ChatGPT messages for later reference.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Collected</h2>
  
  <h3>Local-Only Storage</h3>
  <p>All your pinned data stays on your device:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pinned messages (only those you manually select)</li>
    <li>Categories and tags you create</li>
    <li>User preferences and settings</li>
  </ul>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <strong>No data is sent to any external server unless you explicitly choose to sync 
    via your own storage account (future feature).</strong>
  </p>

  <h2>Data Not Collected</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>ChatGPT account information</li>
    <li>Conversations stored on OpenAI servers</li>
    <li>Personal identifiers or email</li>
    <li>General browser activity</li>
    <li>Messages you did not manually pin</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Protect Your Data</h2>
  <p>
    We do not access content outside the pinned messages you manually select. Pinboard GPT only reads 
    the specific messages you choose to pin and stores them locally in your browser.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>None.</strong> Pinboard GPT operates independently without relying on external analytics or servers.
  </p>

  <h2>Future Sync Feature</h2>
  <p>
    If Pinboard GPT adds a sync feature in the future, users will have the option to store data 
    in their own cloud accounts (e.g., Google Drive, Dropbox). A separate privacy disclosure will 
    be provided at that time.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy inquiries, contact us at:<br />
    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dps.manit@gmail.com">dps.manit@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p><a href="/privacy">‚Üê Back to Master Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
